1
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,760
Slow down.

2
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,120
Slow down. Don't fall.

3
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:31,120
Slow down.

4
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,120
Come here. Do you want something to eat?

5
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:57,560
Slow down.

6
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:01,120
How about we weave a flower crown?

7
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,280
You pick a pretty flower,

8
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,280
and I'll weave it for you, okay?

9
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,320
Take off!

10
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:05,280
Slow down.

11
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,160
Slow down. Be careful.

12
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,800
Look, is this pretty?

13
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:10,600
Slow down.

14
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,040
Lili, fly me.

15
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,880
Okay, I'll fly you.

16
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:14,640
Fly you.

17
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:16,720
Take off!

18
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:19,450
Look at the wreath I made for you, isn't it pretty?

19
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,200
Just look at the wreath.

20
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,400
Fly me,

21
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:23,240
fly me, Lili.

22
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:23,920
Okay.

23
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:25,920
Be careful!

24
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,700
Somebody help! Come here, quick!

25
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:34,920
Taking off!

26
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,500
Where are you hurt?

27
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,280
Where did you get hurt?

28
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,079
Does it hurt?

29
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,520
Are you hurt?

30
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:47,560
I'm flying!

31
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:48,520
Take off!

32
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:49,960
Flying away!

33
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,040
Who sent you?

34
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:55,640
Mr. Lu,

35
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:57,240
it's a misunderstanding.

36
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,400
Get out of the Lu family house right now.

37
00:02:59,400 --> 00:02:59,880
Go!

38
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:00,600
Mr. Lu.

39
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,920
Flying away!

40
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,760
Mr. Lu, the afternoon meetings are over.

41
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:06,160
The meeting minutes have been sent to your email,

42
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,960
and the staff have been seen off.

43
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,210
Starting tomorrow,

44
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:11,760
meetings with Zhongtai Real Estate and Rongxin Technology

45
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,090
will all be held at home.

46
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:14,780
Okay, I'll go notify them.

47
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:16,440
But arranging everything at home,

48
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:17,840
won't it be too much trouble for you?

49
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,570
I don't mind the trouble at all.

50
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,680
Given Zhixia's current condition,

51
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:23,320
I have to stay by her side.

52
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:24,400
Yes.

53
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,320
Mom.

54
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:33,740
I don't think Shen Zhixia is pretending.

55
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:36,170
She fell so hard during the day.

56
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,120
And yet she smiled like a fool.

57
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:39,680
A fool?

58
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:43,370
Could a fool dodge from such a close distance?

59
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,560
Blind luck.

60
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,680
She was just lucky.

61
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:49,520
Shen Zhixia is extremely cunning.

62
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:52,540
This isn't the first time she's played the fool.

63
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:54,840
How do you know she's not acting?

64
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,680
Exactly, Mom.

65
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:04,160
But this Lu Jingheng

66
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,890
treats her like a treasure now.

67
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:08,180
He wishes he could tie her to his belt.

68
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,970
I have no chance to get close to her.

69
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,740
If we don't succeed this time,

70
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:17,480
it'll be hard to test her again.

71
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,880
What's the rush?

72
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,050
Have you forgotten?

73
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:23,160
Your brother is a busy man.

74
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,080
He has to keep an eye on the company,

75
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,320
and manage his woman.

76
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:28,520
Even a tiger needs to take a nap.

77
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:30,640
I don't believe

78
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:32,159
this Shen Zhixia

79
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:34,600
can stay this lucky forever.

80
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,520
Lili,

81
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,000
are you thirsty?

82
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,960
Coming.

83
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:49,080
Water.

84
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,880
Give me the water.

85
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:52,720
I'll take my sister-in-law back to her room later.

86
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,360
But...

87
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:56,520
Water. Thirsty.

88
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,780
You're thirsty, Sister-in-law?

89
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:05,880
Water.

90
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:15,880
Drink.

91
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,240
You drank from it.

92
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,280
Water.

93
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,000
Wait a minute.

94
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:25,680
Water.

95
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,480
Tang Lili is unbelievable,

96
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:28,010
giving you such cold water.

97
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:30,210
Isn't she worried about your stomach?

98
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:40,120
Drink it.

99
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,159
Hot!

100
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,520
Hot!

101
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:50,480
It's okay, sister-in-law.

102
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,610
I'll wipe it for you.

103
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,760
It won't hurt after wiping.

104
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:57,680
It won't hurt after wiping.

105
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,200
Wipe it,

106
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,240
and it won't hurt.

107
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,880
Get away.

108
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:07,160
I'm sorry. I didn't mean to.

109
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:14,640
Take off.

110
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:15,520
Take off.

111
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:16,720
Sorry, sister-in-law.

112
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,560
Take off,

113
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,360
brother.

114
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,360
Get out.

115
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,840
Bye.

116
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:35,560
Are you sure her reaction isn't fake?

117
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:37,920
Instinctive reactions

118
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:38,850
cannot be faked.

119
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,440
If that's really the case,

120
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,940
there's no harm in keeping her for a few days.

121
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,880
Mom's years of painstaking efforts weren't in vain.

122
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:51,520
We can finally rest easy.

123
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:54,800
Why do I still feel uneasy?

124
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,280
What if she suddenly recovers

125
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,880
and remembers the past?

126
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,810
Then let's keep her crazy forever.

127
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:07,040
It's best if she can't even recognize Lu Jingheng.

128
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:09,440
So crazy she can never ruin our plans again.

129
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,120
Does it hurt?

130
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,210
Be good. Don't move.

131
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,980
It won't hurt after I apply the medicine.

132
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,240
You wear it.

133
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,800
It looks good on you.

134
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,440
It looks great.

135
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:37,520
Bear with it. It will be over soon.

136
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,120
All done.

137
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:00,440
Jingheng.

138
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:02,200
Don't frown.

139
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:04,160
It doesn't look good.

140
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,370
You're frowning again.

141
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:18,250
If you hadn't lost your memory,

142
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,680
you could have protected yourself.

143
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,640
Now, when you need me most,

144
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:24,720
I failed to protect you.

145
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:48,480
Rest early.

146
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,610
I'm right next door.

147
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:51,940
Call me anytime if you need anything.

148
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:32,840
Lu Jingheng, thank you for protecting me.

149
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,880
But I can't keep hiding behind you.

150
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,280
Some things must be settled,

151
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:37,320
and some debts must be collected.

152
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:39,240
It's time I faced them myself.

153
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,940
I'm off work. Come back tomorrow.

154
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,140
We can talk about it tomorrow.

155
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,640
What poor quality.

156
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:05,080
We'll talk tomorrow. Do you hear me?

157
00:10:10,520 --> 00:10:11,280
Who is it?

158
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:19,800
Don't you remember me?

159
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:21,120
Y-you. Who are you?

160
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:23,040
This is a hospital.

161
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,560
This is the psychiatric department.

162
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:25,720
If you play tricks here,

163
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:29,480
you'll be locked up as a psychopath.

164
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:32,680
I am your patient.

165
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:36,440
You prescribed medicine for me back then.

166
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:40,600
And you killed me with your own hands.

167
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:48,960
How could that be?

168
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:52,280
I am your patient.

169
00:10:53,280 --> 00:10:55,440
Is it because I jumped off the building

170
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,240
and ruined my face?

171
00:10:58,080 --> 00:11:00,920
W-what are you talking about?

172
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:03,360
I don't understand a word.

173
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,960
Don't you recognize me?

174
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:14,360
Is it because I jumped off the building

175
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,520
and ruined my face,

176
00:11:15,520 --> 00:11:18,200
so you can't recognize me?

177
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:21,440
It-It's Lin Hui.

178
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:24,160
Oh, my God.

179
00:11:28,920 --> 00:11:29,800
Y-you.

180
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:32,080
Aren't you dead?

181
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:35,000
Yes, I am.

182
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:38,240
I died for no reason.

183
00:11:38,640 --> 00:11:41,400
I died so unjustly.

184
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,880
It's none of my business.

185
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:45,410
It has nothing to do with me.

186
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:48,600
Yes, someone forced me to do it.

187
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:52,760
Who forced you?

188
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:55,480
Mr. Shen, Shen Jingyao.

189
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:59,240
He told me to increase the dosage

190
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,280
and change the medical records.

191
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:03,040
He ordered all of it.

192
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:09,080
Who forced you?

193
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:09,920
Shen Jingyao.

194
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,520
Who forced you?

195
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:14,080
Shen, Shen Jingyao.

196
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,920
Shen Jingyao, Shen Jingyao.

197
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:16,920
Who forced you?

198
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,040
Shen Jingyao.

199
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:21,360
All right, all right, Dr. Li.

200
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,760
That's enough.

201
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:27,840
I think Dr. Li has a guilty conscience.

202
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:30,760
Do you really believe in ghosts?

203
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:35,120
Open your eyes and look at me.

204
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:36,520
I won't look. I won't look.

205
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:38,280
I know I'll die if I look.

206
00:12:38,880 --> 00:12:40,160
That's enough.

207
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:48,080
It's you.

208
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:56,360
Tell me more about it.

209
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:02,600
I'll talk.

210
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:05,740
I'll tell you everything.

211
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:15,480
When your mother was first admitted to the hospital,

212
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:17,520
she only had mild depression.

213
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:21,560
With emotional stability

214
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,760
and simple medical intervention,

215
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:25,600
she could make a full

216
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:27,840
recovery.

217
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:31,400
Shen Jingyao approached me

218
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:34,760
and gave me 500,000

219
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:38,720
to secretly increase your mother's dosage

220
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:41,200
at every follow-up visit.

221
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:44,920
He also made me emphasize in the medical records

222
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:48,480
that her condition was erratic

223
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:52,840
and that she had severe suicidal tendencies.

224
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:57,720
Later, the dosage was so high

225
00:13:58,360 --> 00:14:01,160
that your mother started having hallucinations.

226
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:04,920
Not only did Shen Jingyao refuse to let me reduce the dosage,

227
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:06,000
he also...

228
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:08,080
He also asked me to entice you...

229
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:10,720
No, guide your mother.

230
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,080
Guide her into thinking that

231
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:17,320
living was torture

232
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:20,840
and that suicide was the only way out.

